141
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:13,960
Yes.

142
00:08:21,630 --> 00:08:24,160
That arsonist has been
hiding in Shencheng,

143
00:08:24,270 --> 00:08:25,390
causing my people

144
00:08:25,390 --> 00:08:27,120
