148
00:08:34,390 --> 00:08:35,790
A barefoot doctor named Lin?

149
00:08:44,630 --> 00:08:45,720
I discovered the man

150
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:47,360
who analyzed medicine for Feng Jingyun

151
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:48,870
