Lin Guangyao to light.

171
00:09:34,550 --> 00:09:36,080
I wiped him out.

172
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:38,320
It doesn't matter who's behind him.

173
00:09:38,390 --> 00:09:39,790
If anyone dares to back him,

174
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:42,000
